examples.en: I had to barter with the locals for food.
The women in the market are bartering hens for milk.
They bartered their grain for salt.
We had no money so we had to live by barter.
The tribes use a system of barter.
The women are bartering with their neighbours.
Trading was carried out under a barter system.
The captain went to the enemy camp to barter for the prisoner's life.
The explorers used blankets and other supplies for barter to get food from the native people.
